lead_paragraph: German engineering group Siemens is in final stage talks to sell its 50 percent stake in a household goods joint venture to partner Robert Bosch [ROBG.UL], two sources familiar with the matter said on Wednesday.

headline.main: Siemens in Talks to Sell Stake in Household Goods Venture to Bosch: Sources
